1. Videla sam *polje* žita na putu do grada. (I saw a *field* of wheat on my way to the city.)
2. Na *polju* se nalaze farmeri koji obrađuju zemlju. (Farmers who cultivate the land are located in the *field*.)
3. Zid je bio visok, ali je Nemanja bez problema skočio preko *police*. (The wall was high, but Nemanja jumped over the *ledge* without any problem.)
4. Ona ima vitke *noge* koje joj stoje odlično u štiklama. (She has slender *legs* that look great in high heels.)
5. Moj komšija drži veliki *štap* za pecanje u svom podrumu. (My neighbor keeps a large *fishing rod* in his basement.)
6. Slušala sam kako su *policajci* razgovarali o pljački koja se dogodila. (I overheard *police officers* talking about a robbery that had happened.)
7. Tog jutra, snežna *padavina* je pokrila celo *polje*. (That morning, the snow *fall* covered the entire *field*.)
8. Na putu do posla, vozila sam pored *električnih* *bandera*. (On my way to work, I drove past *electric* *poles*.)
9. Baka je na svoju *palicu* stavila šarenu maramu kako bi je lakše pronašla. (Grandma put a colorful scarf on her *walking stick* to make it easier to find.)
10. U parku se nalazi *stolica* na kojoj možete sedeti i uživati u prirodi. (There is a *chair* in the park where you can sit and enjoy nature.)